cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.NE 

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with language models. It could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as it uses neural networks and topic modeling. Additionally, it could be categorized under cs.IR (Information Retrieval) as it deals with document context and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as it uses neural networks.
